# sprites.pal — Sprite palettes (shared across all levels)
# 4 sub-palettes × 4 colors = 16 NES color IDs
# Color 0 = transparent (use $0F black as placeholder)

# Sub-palette 0: Player (Alconario)
0F 36 16 06

# Sub-palette 1: Enemies (Goombas, Koopas)
0F 27 17 07

# Sub-palette 2: Items / Fire / Coins
0F 28 16 30

# Sub-palette 3: HUD / Text
0F 30 10 00
